{"tid":2136222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【金燦傻教授：咩叫雙贏？！就係支那贏完又贏】美軍美國號兩棲攻擊艦進入東海","createTime":"2020-08-02T03:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T03:57:55.000Z","uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"210399e88c81f81a7b8a0a9f7824ca1aac1d1177","tid":2136222,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"美軍美國號兩棲攻擊艦進入東海<br />\n國際 發佈時間 2020-08-01 15:51最後更新時間 2020-08-01 15:51<br />\n<br />\n北大海洋戰略研究中心平台指，早前在東海活動的美軍列根號航空母艦打擊群，返回日本橫須賀母港；另一支美國號兩棲攻擊艦，則離開日本佐世保海軍基地，進入東海。 美國號兩棲攻擊艦去年底進駐佐世保美軍海軍基地，加入美軍第7艦隊，提升美軍在亞太區的空中攻擊力量。美國號是美軍最新型兩棲攻擊艦的首艦，排水量4.5萬噸，可搭載F35B隱形戰機。"},{"pid":"551514f36202a28fb6fe948e97b9c61243fb86a9","tid":2136222,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2350110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2350110&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=cf510aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2350110</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"2cba605b77be6d7552ba383fcda3e2ae2ac0e094","tid":2136222,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/3o17kd6v05q31.jpg?auto=webp&amp;s=3a94aa69fe94704218dbf5d156dcf81957221b84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2F3o17kd6v05q31.jpg%3Fauto%3Dwebp%26s%3D3a94aa69fe94704218dbf5d156dcf81957221b84&h=fe1c66d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJ3KgNnUYAAmBX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEJ3KgNnUYAAmBX8.jpg&h=a411987a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}